---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const legalEmail =
  import.meta.env.PUBLIC_CONTACT_EMAIL ??
  import.meta.env.CONTACT_TO_EMAIL ??
  "kontakt@sebastijanbogdan.com";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy | Sebastijan Bogdan"
  description="Information about personal data processing."
>
  <section>
    <h1>Privacy</h1>

    <p>
      This page explains how personal data is processed on sebastijanbogdan.com,
      especially when using the contact form.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
    <p>
      Sebastijan Bogdan<br />
      [Add street and number]<br />
      [Add postal code and city]<br />
      Email: <a href={`mailto:${legalEmail}`}>{legalEmail}</a>
    </p>

    <h2>2. What data is processed?</h2>
    <p>
      When using the contact form, the following data may be processed: name
      (optional), email (optional), phone (optional), message (required), and
      technical security data (IP address, timestamp, rate-limit metadata,
      and anti-spam token).
    </p>

    <h2>3. Purpose and legal basis</h2>
    <p>
      Data is processed to handle your inquiry and to protect the form against
      abuse. Legal basis is Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (pre-contractual communication)
      and Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in secure operation).
    </p>

    <h2>4. Retention period</h2>
    <p>
      Contact form requests are not stored in a separate application database.
      Messages are delivered only by email and deleted after 180 days at the
      latest, unless legal retention obligations apply.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Recipients and processors</h2>
    <p>
      Service providers are used for hosting, email delivery, anti-spam checks,
      and rate limiting. This includes Vercel, Resend, Cloudflare Turnstile,
      and Upstash. Processing may also take place outside the EU.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You have rights to access, rectification, deletion, restriction,
      portability, and objection in certain cases. You also have the right
      to file a complaint with a supervisory authority.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Privacy contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, contact
      <a href={`mailto:${legalEmail}`}>{legalEmail}</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
